Justice for Jane Clough and her Family.
Janes Killer Jonathan Vass is serving 30 years in Jail for her Brutal Murder but he has not been convicted of the heinous Sexual assaults Charges made against him by Jane.

The family have not been given Justice as this man has got away with torturing their daughter before taking her away from them with absolutely no remorse.

Please sign this petition to make your government aware that you will not stand for misjudgments that allow innocent people to go on living in fear of their attacker and in some very tragic cases having their life taken by their attacker.

Get justice for Jane and her family and stop other people becoming a victim
